Provenance, neutrality & governance
-------------------------------------
capsule-anchor is developed by Action State Group, Inc. and published as
open-source software (Apache-2.0). It implements a neutral, vendor-free SCITT
Transparency Service (draft-ietf-scitt-architecture) with RFC9162 (RFC6962)
Certificate-Transparency Merkle proofs and COSE Receipt issuance.

The codebase is product-free — no commercial features, tier gates, or
metering are present. It is designed with a clean transfer path to a neutral
standards body or foundation donation when the ecosystem matures.

